### **DMN Elements and Representation**

| Element                        | DMN Standard Shape                                      | Connector                               |
| ------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------- |
| Decision                       | Rectangle with slightly rounded corners                 | Solid arrow for Information Requirement |
| Input Data                     | Fully rounded rectangle                                 | Solid arrow to Decisions                |
| Business Knowledge Model (BKM) | Rectangle with top-right corner cut (dog-ear)           | Dashed arrow for Knowledge Requirement  |
| Knowledge Source               | Rectangle with folded top-right corner (document shape) | Dotted arrow for Authority Requirement  |

